strings.Value: "So much suffering... I can't bear to see them!"
"You haven't been yourself lately, Tristian. Stop punishing yourself. You do all you can. Surely you know this."
"You burden is heavy. To attempt to save someone, yet fail... I know well that feeling."
"It's touching to see you care so much. You must be really sorry for anyone who dies without a chance of becoming a servant of your goddess!"
